{"abstract": "Mata Amritanandamayi, known as Amma, is a globe-trotting guru who embraces the masses \u2014 and a get-it-done management style for her charities.", "web_url": "https://www.nytimes.com/2013/05/26/business/ammas-multifaceted-empire-built-on-hugs.html", "snippet": "Mata Amritanandamayi, known as Amma, is a globe-trotting guru who embraces the masses \u2014 and a get-it-done management style for her charities.", "lead_paragraph": "THERE are entourages \u2014 and then there is the retinue of Mata Amritanandamayi, a 59-year-old Indian guru known simply as Amma, or \u201cmother.\u201d On Friday, she began a two-month North American tour during which she will be accompanied by 275 volunteers. They plan to ride in four buses across the continent from Bellevue, Wash., to Marlborough, Mass., visiting 11 cities, including New York. And at each stop along the way, Amma will sit on stage for 15 hours at a stretch, greeting her thousands of devotees. ", "print_section": "BU", "print_page": "1", "source": "The New York Times", "multimedia": [{"rank": 0, "subtype": "xlarge", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2013/05/26/business/26-AMMA/26-AMMA-articleLarge.jpg", "height": 452, "width": 600, "subType": "xlarge", "crop_name": "articleLarge", "legacy": {"xlarge": "images/2013/05/26/business/26-AMMA/26-AMMA-articleLarge.jpg", "xlargewidth": 600, "xlargeheight": 452}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "jumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2013/05/26/business/26-AMMA/26-AMMA-jumbo.jpg", "height": 771, "width": 1024, "subType": "jumbo", "crop_name": "jumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "superJumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2013/05/26/business/26-AMMA/26-AMMA-superJumbo.jpg", "height": 1542, "width": 2048, "subType": "superJumbo", "crop_name": "superJumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "thumbnail", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "image